title: Lynda - Landscape Photography with Telephoto Lenses with Justin
description:
Lynda - Landscape Photography with Telephoto Lenses with Justin Reznick

FYI : This Course will be good to the Best for DL within 30 days after has been posed, after that it might not be good DL already, please do me favour to continue seeding to keep this torrent alive.

Course Duration:51m 57s Level: Intermediate Updated: Feb 26, 2016 
| Uploaded in Apr 5, 2016 by 2boweb

Get up close and personal with nature. Explore the creative options that telephoto lenses provide in landscape photography. This targeted group of photography tips is for anyone who is interested in isolating subjects, compressing distance, shooting panoramas, or creating abstract and impressionistic images with telephoto lenses. Justin Reznick provides simple guidelines for more effective images, and helps photographers find new uses for this great piece of gear
